<p>æç¤ºï¼š</p>

<p>costs.length == n</p>

<p>1 &lt;= n &lt;= 105</p>

<p>1 &lt;= costs[i] &lt;= 105</p>

<p>1 &lt;= coins &lt;= 108</p>

<h3 id="æ€è·¯">æ€è·¯</h3>

<p>â€œä¹°å°½å¯èƒ½å¤šçš„é›ªç³•â€ï¼Œæ’åºåé€‰æ‹©æœ€ä¾¿å®œçš„å³å¯ï¼Œä¸æ˜¯èƒŒåŒ…é—®é¢˜ã€‚</p>

<h3 id="ä»£ç ">ä»£ç </h3>

<pre><code class="language-c++">class Solution {
public:
    int maxIceCream(vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; costs, int coins) {
        sort(costs.begin(),costs.end());
        if(costs[0] &gt; coins){
            return 0;
        }
        int value = 0;
        int count = 0;
        for(int i=0;i &lt;costs.size(); i++){
               value = value + costs[i];
               if(value &lt;= coins){
                   count++;
               }else{
                   break;
               }
        }
        return count;
    }
};
</code></pre>

